quote><br />\n去到最後一刻先買唔通仲想有靚位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98c236a5d959adde02a58b0ad63584e4aaf9685c","tid":193001,"uid":64576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T11:26:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實比其他國家 香港算好平</blockquote><br />\n但係比起其他國家，香港人工都好平呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n歐洲上網買戲飛不知幾方便，直接debit card 扣數零手續費<br />\n根本無人會排隊買飛<br />\n可能香港人labour cost低<br />\n公司情願請多幾個最低工資都唔搞好個online system <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n高登又係咁<br />\n過system 90年代。<br />\n<br />\n用到就得，揸數佬心態。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係香港問題，香港商家佬覺得用到就算。<br />\nIT infra使撚咁勁咁前衛咩，呢啲investment係無撚謂。<br />\n有一日成個system死咗咪先再算囉。</blockquote><br />\n有時唔想比手續費，唔想特登落街買<br />\n真係情願唔睇<br />\n唔明點解大陸做到既野 香港都無</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n雖然我係憎大陸人，<br />\n但其實大陸人睇嘢個觀念係闊過香港人我覺得。<br />\n<br />\n你見人地識得放長線釣香港呢條魚就知，<br />\n香港啲商家佬、政府就淨係識得舐人鞋底，<br />\n見呢刻有錢賺、有利益就賺咗先，<br />\n其實落咗搭都唔知。<br />\n<br />\n人地第日一鑊撬起你就直接收皮。</blockquote><br />\n小心有癲狗咬你"},{"pid":"03a9ccb35f73eb6d5884e8e2efbcf50b51013c5e","tid":193001,"uid":17067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T21:50:12.000Z","msg":"照比"},{"pid":"1f606746264e615a162796d49a5aa7b7fbb25564","tid":193001,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T22:10:56.000Z","msg":"長者廿五蚊張飛好抵，而家去親睇戲都係長者觀眾佔多數。"},{"pid":"58ce37767dffa0ee0fc92ce6f6e5200016747c70","tid":193001,"uid":80736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T22:11:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>都唔明，都唔洗人手點解要收手續費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"621fd23352323f69fc3fb797e8ec578bc7aa8af9","tid":193001,"uid":2500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T23:35:20.000Z","msg":"所以而家真係好想睇先會去睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9c0e9ebf82c28e0da8d9d5fb8b6e36bd930481f","tid":193001,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T23:39:24.000Z","msg":"唔好睇囉"},{"pid":"c5ceded27b178167df3f4f290862b7d2ec034dcd","tid":193001,"uid":3573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T23:42:53.000Z","msg":"啲手續費仲唔係比it狗嘅?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9835a361f78aa0e7d0003531e32b7b9867a77215","tid":193001,"uid":44323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T23:46:48.000Z","msg":"唔幫襯咪得 上面個d 又要俾又要屌做乜撚"},{"pid":"5a577697be33cbe6941922661cc7a5c96313f559","tid":193001,"uid":8086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T23:58:18.000Z","msg":"睇戲真係好撚貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13937fb9fae62cff747556d9a7594d1b4150e09b","tid":193001,"uid":61443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T23:59:58.000Z","msg":"仲要逐張收 $10<br />\n有啲港產片想睇都冇動力 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n月薪 : 10k"},{"pid":"443885942b640c645b70faab22fdeb18c7a95986","tid":193001,"uid":99911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T00:18:15.000Z","msg":"上面咪講左留位囉 比walk-in嘅人早一步買喎 人地臨開場前幾十分鐘先排隊 你可能早幾粒鐘 甚至早幾日買 俾多少少錢都算合理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3aaa6c3af11e8eb1ddcaf38045d367bc88fcde6","tid":193001,"uid":56561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T00:25:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>都唔明，都唔洗人手點解要收手續費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nIT 狗唔洗食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"432da2e8999756278f5a95e9f61953037f2d4bdf","tid":193001,"uid":56123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T00:31:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大陸睇戲上網訂飛仲會減價</blockquote><br />\n理性啲睇<br />\n香港呢方面真心差<br />\n<br />\n等睇我畀人屌 叫我死返強國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大陸同香港相反，walkin係要比正價，網上買優惠係30-50%</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌，大部分野公司都推廣網上訂，可以慳人手，好多仲有特別優惠，係個戲飛冇優惠不特止，仲要手續費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e774e4f9a0a399e1a8b5c1898201fe8cbbb86130","tid":193001,"uid":12599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T00:34:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲要逐張收 $10<br />\n有啲港產片想睇都冇動力 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n月薪 : 10k</blockquote><br />\n跟本係暴利,正常所有野轉左電子系統成本一定低過人手,而家個system獨市,除非有第二間公司想搞呢個市場(技術層面睇唔係太難),如果唔會佢只會年年加<br />\n<br />\n你唔上網買咩?好呀你自己出去戲院買囉,不過同一個院線係買唔到另一間戲院既飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你想要靚位?上網買每張補多$10啦"},{"pid":"747a9da530f4cae561fcd89f15c44465f26dd3d0","tid":193001,"uid":7155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T00:41:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>仲要逐張收 $10<br />\n有啲港產片想睇都冇動力 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n月薪 : 10k</blockquote><br />\n跟本係暴利,正常所有野轉左電子系統成本一定低過人手,而家個system獨市,除非有第二間公司想搞呢個市場(技術層面睇唔係太難),如果唔會佢只會年年加<br />\n<br />\n你唔上網買咩?好呀你自己出去戲院買囉,不過同一個院線係買唔到另一間戲院既飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你想要靚位?上網買每張補多$10啦</blockquote><br />\n呢樣真係on9 ，明明佢地個電腦系統都係相連架啦<br />\n點解同一間公司都買唔到另一間戲院既飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港人人忙到嘔，仲有時間特登去果間戲院？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有時真係覺得香港無人入場睇戲係佢地自己攞黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93888480a2e45848d2841236fc6657d9ddffad86","tid":193001,"uid":2950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T01:24:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>搵你唔駛排隊嘅時間，你即時買飛，咪個位咪理想啲。<br />\n<br />\n根本就係經濟心理嘢，唔係慳成本嘅問題。</blockquote><br />\n點解其他國家網上買飛平過walk in?</blockquote><br />\n香港交通太方便<br />\n老闆：幫你慳左來回車錢仲想點？<br />\n<br />\n鬼佬要渣車來回買飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解其他國家要渣車來回但網上買飛平過walk in?"},{"pid":"f01bf9ffa064d4dc37f9e255a4fb146f4dd432b3","tid":193001,"uid":6352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T01:32:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實比其他國家 香港算好平</blockquote><br />\n但係比起其他國家，香港人工都好平呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n英國最低工資就7鎊， <br />\n睇場戲就8-9 鎊<br />\n香港最低工資三十幾蚊， <br />\n睇戲成舊水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇戲係種不必要娛樂，攞黎同最低工資比，毫無意義。"},{"pid":"c8e7db2ebb8875f5e755ad10f41c0e92389ed72e","tid":193001,"uid":105130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T01:46:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同一套戲最平六十幾最貴舊幾兩舊，想平定貴根本係有得選擇。</blockquote><br />\n有兩間平既都係屯門，又會屌蝕車費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屯門個兩間睇戲環境唔好, 因為好多人講野. <br />\n<br />\n係平過出面好多, 40幾50左右, 但會有人同你講解劇情, <br />\n又有人傾電話"},{"pid":"7c7914dbd70cd6f67fb8f8248261d2bba97432f1","tid":193001,"uid":4349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T01:51:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實比其他國家 香港算好平</blockquote><br />\n但係比起其他國家，香港人工都好平呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n英國最低工資就7鎊， <br />\n睇場戲就8-9 鎊<br />\n香港最低工資三十幾蚊， <br />\n睇戲成舊水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇戲係種不必要娛樂，攞黎同最低工資比，毫無意義。</blockquote><br />\n總有柒頭跳出黎幫商家含撚<br />\nA to A B to B點撚樣無意義呀<br />\n唔計呢樣計食, 香港最低工資都係收皮啦"},{"pid":"a0c720303f609c75c8233724d7d145083e5606b1","tid":193001,"uid":9115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T01:53:21.000Z","msg":"覺唔覺睇場戲都要睇價錢真係好撚on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d336576298e5700ea64b5a0a0a3a7c6d3fcfdbf","tid":193001,"uid":52265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T02:08:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>當慳左一來一回個交通費<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n交通費有時仲貴</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n宜家好似9蚊張<br />\n<br />\n過海買咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}